#CHIP K051649
#CLOCK 1789772

; K051649 (SCC) - Wavetable Synthesis Test
;
; The SCC has 5 channels, each with a 32-byte signed waveform and
; 12-bit frequency divider. This test exercises the wavetable synthesis
; across all 5 channels with a simple chord and melody.

#TRACK 0

TEMPO 120

; Channel 0: melody
c4 d4 e4 f4

g4 a4 b4 c5

; Channel 1: harmony (third above)
e4 f4 g4 a4

; Channel 2: inner voice
g4 . a4 . b4 .

; Channel 3: bass
c3 . d3 . e3 .

; Channel 4: bass pedal
c2 . . . . .

; All together
c4 & e4 & g4

r2

#END
